Package frc.robot

Record Class ChoreoTraj

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
frc.robot.ChoreoTraj
public record ChoreoTraj(String name, OptionalInt segment, double totalTimeSecs, edu.wpi.first.math.geometry.Pose2d initialPoseBlue, edu.wpi.first.math.geometry.Pose2d endPoseBlue) extends Record
A class containing the name, start pose, end pose, and total time of every Choreo trajectory. This prevents your code from referencing deleted or misspelled trajectories, and removes the need for JSON parsing to load a trajectory's essential data. DO NOT MODIFY THIS FILE YOURSELF! It is automatically generated by Choreo.
